            <h3>State-of-the-Art Facilities</h3>
            <p>Aatura Hospital is equipped with advanced technology and state-of-the-art facilities to support our Nephrology Department's efforts. From our dedicated dialysis units to our on-site laboratory and imaging services, we have the resources needed to deliver high-quality kidney care to our patients. Our hospital also has access to transplant centers for patients requiring kidney transplantation, ensuring seamless coordination of care throughout the transplant process.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content3">
