            <h3>Patient-Centered Care</h3>
            <p>At Aatura Hospital, we prioritize patient-centered care, focusing on the individual needs and preferences of each patient. Our nephrologists take the time to listen to patients' concerns, answer their questions, and involve them in decision-making regarding their kidney health. We believe in empowering patients with knowledge and support to actively participate in their treatment plan and achieve the best possible outcomes.</p>
        </div>
